Title: 系统架构
Describe: Deep Agents 的分层架构、依赖方向和运行时拓扑
------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
分层架构图

[Description]
从用户代码到 LLM 调用的完整分层。每一层有明确的职责边界和扩展点，依赖方向严格自上而下。

[UML]
@startuml
left to right direction

package "Layer 1: User Code" as L1 {
  component "Application" as App
  component "Configuration" as Cfg
}

package "Layer 2: SDK API" as L2 {
  component "create_deep_agent()" as CDA
  component "HarnessProfile" as HP
  component "ProviderProfile" as PP
}

package "Layer 3: Middleware Stack" as L3 {
  component "TodoListMiddleware" as Todo
  component "SkillsMiddleware" as Skills
  component "FilesystemMiddleware" as FSM
  component "SubAgentMiddleware" as SAM
  component "SummarizationMiddleware" as Sum
  component "MemoryMiddleware" as Mem
  component "HumanInTheLoopMiddleware" as HITL
}

package "Layer 4: Backends" as L4 {
  component "BackendProtocol" as BP
  component "StateBackend" as SB
  component "SandboxBackend" as Sand
}

package "Layer 5: LangGraph Runtime" as L5 {
  component "CompiledStateGraph" as CSG
  component "DeltaChannel" as DC
  component "Checkpointer" as CK
}

package "Layer 6: LLM Providers" as L6 {
  component "Anthropic API" as Anth
  component "OpenAI API" as OAI
  component "Google API" as Goog
}

L1 --> L2
L2 --> L3
L3 --> L4
L2 --> L5
L5 --> L6
@enduml

[Detail]
**各层职责**:

| 层次 | 职责 | 扩展点 |
|------|------|--------|
| Layer 1 | 用户应用代码和配置 | 自定义工具、system prompt |
| Layer 2 | SDK 公开 API 和 Profile 系统 | HarnessProfile 注册 |
| Layer 3 | 功能中间件（文件、子任务、摘要等） | 自定义 AgentMiddleware |
| Layer 4 | 文件系统和执行后端 | 实现 BackendProtocol |
| Layer 5 | LangGraph 运行时引擎 | Checkpointer / Store |
| Layer 6 | LLM 提供商 API | BaseChatModel 实现 |

**依赖方向规则**:
- 严格自上而下：上层只依赖下层接口，不反向引用
- Layer 3（中间件）通过 Layer 4（后端）访问文件系统，不直接调用 OS API
- Layer 5 通过 `BaseChatModel` 抽象与 Layer 6 解耦

**运行时数据流**:
- 请求方向：L1 → L2 → L3 → L5 → L6（LLM 调用）
- 响应方向：L6 → L5 → L3（工具执行）→ L5 → L6（下一轮）→ ... → L1

------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
包间依赖架构

[Description]
8 个包的依赖方向和版本约束。所有包以 SDK 为中心，呈星型拓扑。

[UML]
@startuml
left to right direction

component "deepagents\n(SDK v0.6.7)" as SDK #LightBlue

component "deepagents-code\n(TUI REPL)" as Code
component "deepagents-cli\n(Deploy)" as CLI
component "deepagents-acp\n(Protocol)" as ACP
component "deepagents-evals\n(Evaluation)" as Evals

component "langchain-daytona\n(Sandbox)" as Daytona
component "langchain-modal\n(Cloud)" as Modal
component "langchain-quickjs\n(JS)" as QJS
component "langchain-runloop\n(Sandbox)" as Runloop

Code --> SDK : "==0.6.7\n(exact pin)"
CLI --> SDK : ">=0.6.0"
ACP --> SDK : ">=0.6.0"
Evals --> SDK : ">=0.6.0"
Daytona --> SDK : ">=0.5.0"
Modal --> SDK : ">=0.5.0"
QJS --> SDK : ">=0.5.0"
Runloop --> SDK : ">=0.5.0"

SDK --> "langchain-core" : ">=1.4.0,<2.0.0"
SDK --> "langgraph" : runtime
SDK --> "langchain-anthropic" : ">=1.4.3"
@enduml

[Detail]
**版本约束策略差异**:

1. **Code → SDK (exact pin)**:
   - Code 包与 SDK 紧密耦合（依赖内部 API）
   - 必须同步发布，精确匹配版本号
   - 风险：任何 SDK 发布都需要同步更新 Code

2. **CLI/ACP/Evals → SDK (range)**:
   - 仅使用 SDK 公开 API
   - 范围约束允许独立升级
   - 下限取决于使用的 API 引入版本

3. **Partners → SDK (wider range)**:
   - 仅依赖 `BackendProtocol` 接口
   - 接口变更极少，因此范围更宽
   - 各 partner 独立发布不需要等待 SDK

**依赖安全边界**:
- SDK 不 import 任何上层包（单向依赖）
- Partners 之间互不依赖
- `langchain-core` 是最底层共享依赖

------------------------------------------------------------
